JACKSON v. WARDEN OF THE MARYLAND HOUSE OF CORRECTION [App. No. 102,

September Term, 1964.]

Decided February 12, 1965.

*644Before Prescott, C. J., and Hammond, Horney, Marbury, Sybert, OppEnhEimer and Barnes, JJ.

Per Curiam.

For reasons stated in the opinion of Judge Shirley B. Jones below, the application for leave to appeal is hereby denied.
